title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
